+/*
+ * Firmware loader for Adaptec USBXchange / USB2Xchange.
+ *
+ * Uploads device firmware into the Adaptec USBXchange and USB2Xchange
+ * USB --> SCSI dongle.
+ *
+ * Current development and maintenance by:
+ *   (c) 2005 René Rebe <rene@exactcode.de>
